    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It\u2019s got a lot of life left in it and is ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin. Can't wait to see it go to a good home!",
