    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This example retains its Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, ensuring a pure analog driving experience. Critical preventative maintenance has been documented, including a Besian Systems VANOS refresh and a reinforced rear subframe carrier. The variable M differential lock operates silently, and the chassis dynamics remain sharp with refreshed control arm bushings and a precise steering rack. While the finish shows minor road patina, the performance remains uncompromised with a linear power band and exceptional throttle response. A driver-focused machine ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
